{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you [? quickly ?] you see, I was-- remember, I was a teacher already in 1934, that I went to the army, to the officer school in 1935, and then I got my master degree in 1936.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That I was more involved with the personal things in this particular time than thinking about the political aspect what is going on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then when I start to teach in a Jewish gymnasiums-- because that's what I--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1936.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, in this time, I realized that what is going, and we watched much more carefully what was going in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Particularly in 1937, 1938, they start to expel German citizen born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were shifting in-- shipping them from all over Europe, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For example, in 1938, my mother, my father, accepted a family from Moravia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- we kept the whole family 'til they decide to go out because the Czechoslovakia has agreement with-- with Russia in 1938 that they can go through Russia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were sent and permitted by Germans to go over there after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never-- I never heard that a Jew became in a-- in an officer's school in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was the lucky one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I'll tell you what happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was on the university-- because when you became high school graduate, you are eligible to go to officer school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every graduate, regardless of your religion or nationality or what it is, you are a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you can get exempt when you start to study.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got the exemption for five years because takes about five years to graduate university get the degree.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
